Cell["\<\
Only one solution is found... That is likely because, although we specified \
that \[Alpha], \[Beta], \[Gamma], and \[Delta] are positive, we did not \
specify their relative differences.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.979580672400153*^9, 
  3.979580732114024*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b9313a2f-6bf6-4329-8136-\
0c1726fd515d"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

