Cell["\<\
(#2.1.3.6): Alright... so, it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s actually a trivial integral \
and we made it harder than it should have been:\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.990825330852138*^9, 3.9908253517694283`*^9}, 
   3.991780076558236*^9, {3.991780819332107*^9, 
