Cell["\<\
Yeah. It doesn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t do much... Let me see something else (just \
another algebraic rewriting):\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9795741246746397`*^9, 3.979574129442833*^9}, {
  3.9884754037769012`*^9, 3.988475406690255*^9}, {3.988475716185031*^9, 
